title: Flora and Nymphs, with two Gardeners Grafting Trees, after Giulio Romano
description: Landscape scene with figures of Flora, two nymphs and two gardeners. Flora and a nymph seated at left; another nymph asleep in foreground. In background, a nymph, accompanied by two male figures crowning Amor. At right, two gardeners working; in background, a farmer.
name: Print
